---
---

<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="authority-inner fade-up">
      <div class="section-label">About Archway</div>
      <h2>Built for agencies, by the team that works inside them.</h2>
      <p>Archway supports insurance agencies with:</p>
      <div class="authority-services">
        <div class="authority-service">
          <div class="authority-service-icon website">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-5 14H4v-4h11v4zm0-5H4V9h11v4zm5 5h-4V9h4v9z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Website Modernization
        </div>
        <div class="authority-service">
          <div class="authority-service-icon automation">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Marketing Automation
        </div>
        <div class="authority-service">
          <div class="authority-service-icon revenue">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 4.5C7 4.5 2.73 7.61 1 12c1.73 4.39 6 7.5 11 7.5s9.27-3.11 11-7.5c-1.73-4.39-6-7.5-11-7.5zM12 17c-2.76 0-5-2.24-5-5s2.24-5 5-5 5 2.24 5 5-2.24 5-5 5zm0-8c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3 3-1.34 3-3-1.34-3-3-3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Revenue Visibility
        </div>
        <div class="authority-service">
          <div class="authority-service-icon growth">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Cross-Vertical Growth Planning
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="authority-note">This checklist reflects real patterns we see inside agencies every week.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .authority-inner {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .authority-inner > p {
    margin-top: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .authority-services {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .authority-service {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .authority-service:hover {
    border-color: var(--orange);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.08);
  }

  .authority-service-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .authority-service-icon svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  .authority-service-icon.website { background: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.1); }
  .authority-service-icon.website svg { fill: var(--orange); }
  .authority-service-icon.automation { background: rgba(64, 84, 178, 0.1); }
  .authority-service-icon.automation svg { fill: var(--blue); }
  .authority-service-icon.revenue { background: rgba(86, 54, 209, 0.1); }
  .authority-service-icon.revenue svg { fill: #5636d1; }
  .authority-service-icon.growth { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1); }
  .authority-service-icon.growth svg { fill: #22c55e; }

  .authority-note {
    margin-top: 36px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .authority-services {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
